          "I was never the best with words so whenever I have a hard time writing a message, Better BooThang has got me covered! I can pick from one of their premade messages and send it to my boo with no worries. That text I was scared to type will automatically be typed up for me! I can also add or edit the premade text to make them seem more genuine."
