        </blockquote>
      </div>
      <div class="carousel-item">
        <blockquote>
          "Thanks to Better BooThang I've been a better boo! Being a Door Dash Driver I'm always on the road, but with Better BooThang I'm able to send a message from my phone and continue driving to my destination. They even have messages for different occasions! It's as easy as ready, set, go!"
